{"tid":1350651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我而家係度呼籲所有香港人由今日開始出街必備長遮，鐵頭最好","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:25:45.000Z","uid":68080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab848774201c07d1b04aee7d5cb1920460becd7","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:24:06.000Z","msg":"1. 香港夏天天氣極度不穩，隨時可能落雨<br />\n係呢個不穩定既天氣之下，我地帶長遮係合情合理合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天文台黎緊9日既天氣預報都顯示未來9日會有雨，作爲一個有準備既市民，帶遮好合理。<br />\n如果你隔離有女士無帶遮，你仲可以好gentlemen咁問人需唔需要share遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢個情況之下，把遮當然係越大越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />越硬越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 長遮可攻可守<br />\n攻黎講，鐵頭遮你近身又可以當長槍，遠攻又可以當投槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n守更加唔使講，大名鼎鼎既傘陣大家見識過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢係廢左D 但係都叫唔使肉盾硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外膠長遮同唔係鐵骨遮就收皮啦 一下就瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 黑警唔保護市民 咁就由我地真香港人挺身而出<br />\n係愛呢個香港我地先會出黎，我地點可以坐視香港市民俾黑社會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警一家親，黑警唔做我地做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係你無裝備少裝備又點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到尋晚有人開左遮，但係真係少<br />\n大家帶出黎，至少去到危急關頭可以起到路障既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 帶出黎，隨時準備有危難挺身而出<br />\n好似消防一樣，人地都肯做多D出黎維持治安保護市民<br />\n我地就算唔敢衝，我地都要守住等班老弱婦孺走左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋晚大肚婆俾黑社會打既事我唔希望再發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時真係要大家一齊挺身而出<br />\n黑警尋晚拉閘 今晚繼續拉閘<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地香港人要保護香港人<br />\n<br />\nWe Are Hong Kong<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6698683c1c0da0418c177de81da6c277d0fb1bc","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n以後出街帶遮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ce990e7104e218c0db72a1d57ebe2be6f84438","tid":1350651,"uid":113056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiGAQ4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiGAQ4L.jpg&h=f0a80a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/isx4KpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fisx4KpS.jpg&h=87aed0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgsXjYh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgsXjYh.jpg&h=39dcdf13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RY7HbE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RY7HbE.jpg&h=9ae1709d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcF6din.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcF6din.jpg&h=e7688c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Km4F2bK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKm4F2bK.jpg&h=515639af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeb8b4e7799e423a3cca872232272cfcc80518a0","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">另外721黑警無警告下開36槍啊<br />\n頂住啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"784e1142c3f215d282b378e89ae59594c4a1d72f","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"係香港人同我帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8557c9fa884dd894bbb2601c14eda0fcc8060a53","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"前面義士爭取你唔夠膽衝唔夠膽support都算<br />\n後面你連義士既後顧之憂都處理唔到?<br />\n前面義士 我地後面都要保住義士守護既人同事唔好俾黑社會破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真香港人企出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我頂住黑社會保護市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b43ced1384c1a9411128f629e1b57313c6c075f","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"出黎啊"},{"pid":"d66063aec9332aa9472e1ddd3ef5fae9932af089","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:32:38.000Z","msg":"最standard既裝黎"},{"pid":"96bf41af40ca587725c77bbdb0d0ee62f2d4b191","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"遮啊dllm"},{"pid":"78accd4e2f9cc21a8c7a188d85ffacfe96132348","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"有無人唔帶<br />\n唔好下下等人救<br />\n自己香港人自己救"},{"pid":"277a043ae7becb2a8978d3bef3016f49c69d71b6","tid":1350651,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"推啊"}]}